data.description: CHECK OUT THE GREAT NEW PRICE!  Situated on a sprawling acre of land, this home, surrounded by lush greenery and mature trees, offers a serene retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. But don't worry, you are still close to everything in town. The spacious living room boasts hardwood floors, creating a seamless flow to the adjacent dining area. The 1st floor includes a beautifully remodeled full bathroom, as well as French doors leading to the deck, a perfect spot for enjoying the nature surrounding this home. The newly updated kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and butcher block countertops. Head upstairs, where you will find three bedrooms, a massive bonus room, as well as another full bathroom featuring a clawfoot tub and a lovely, tiled floor, this is just another wow factor for this home. Don't wait, call your favorite agent today!
